==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Noiseless
<hw>Noise"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Making, or causing, no noise or
bustle; without noise; silent; <as>as, the <ex>noiseless</ex> foot of
time</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>So <qex>noiseless</qex> would I live.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Noise"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Noise"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>noisemaker</ent>⟦br⟧
